short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: See the weather right on your calendar.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Always be able to plan your events with the weather in mind. 

With gcalweather, you can see your calendar and the weather, right on the same page.

For more information, and to view the source code, see: https://github.com/chrissank/gcalweather
